Package: StreamVAST
Title: Tools for using 'VAST' with stream networks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeremy", "Harris", , "jeremy.harris@dfw.wa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Data formatting for stream networks for use with 'VAST'.
    The package provides tools for manipulating stream lines into a network, 
    associating data with those lines, formatting the data for 'VAST', and plotting
    the output.
